  "date": "2026-07-13T13:57:27Z",
  "subject": "fix: echo-receiver must return 'ok' body - empty 200 fails Alertmanager's Slack parser (review important)",
  "body": "Alertmanager's Slack notifier parser requires a literal 'ok' or JSON {\"ok\":true}\nin the response body. Empty 200 responses cause delivery-failed logs and an\nunresolvable AlertmanagerFailedToSendAlerts critical alert loop.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n"
}
